casebody.data:
Niebuhr, Appellant, v. Schreyer, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November, 1889.) Appeal from special term.

Argued before Larremore, C. J., and Daly and Bookstaver, JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs. For former report, see 2 N. Y. Supp. 413.
